rows.label: tlk43100246_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm starting to get sick of fishing now...
But I dunno what other hobbies are left
that I can do for free...

rows.label: tlk43100246_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm from Torika Alley, me. We don't
get a lot of toys round there.

rows.label: tlk43100246_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Only real fun thing we get to enjoy
is Mymoma Playhouse! It's just up
the stairs.

rows.label: tlk43100246_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Kids can get in for free once a month
in there!

rows.label: tlk43100246_01_msg0005
rows.name: A month's a long time to wait though...
